{"type":null,"faqId":10262,"title":"秘盒M310    快速配置","answer":"<p style=\"text-indent:-3.0cm;\">\n\t<span><span style=\"font-size:7pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>步骤 1<span style=\"font-size:7pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 步骤1 &nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">切换电视信号源</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;使用<b>电视遥控器</b>将电视信号源切换至连接秘盒</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的</span><span>HDMI </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">输入。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-3.0cm;\">\n\t<span><span style=\"font-size:7pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>步骤 2<span style=\"font-size:7pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 步骤2 &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;line-height:1.5;text-indent:-3cm;\">配对蓝牙遥控器</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-3.0cm;\">\n\t<span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;根据电视画面提示，同时按住蓝牙遥控器</span> <span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31127\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" alt=\"\" /></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">和</span> <span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31128\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" alt=\"\" /></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，直到电视画面出现</span> <span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31129\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" alt=\"\" /></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，表示配对成功，再松开按键。<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31130\" alt=\"\" /> </span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-3.0cm;\">\n\t<span><span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>步骤 1<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 步骤3 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;text-indent:-3cm;\">连接无线网络</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-3.0cm;\">\n\t<span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">根据电视画面提示，选择您要连接的无线网络，将秘盒连接至该无线网络。当电视画面出现<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31135\" alt=\"\" /><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">表示连网成功。</span></span><span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31132\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">您也可以选择</span><span>WPS</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">方式连接家庭无线网络。</span><span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">首先请用蓝牙遥控器选择</span><span>“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">请选取</span><span>WPS”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。然后在两分钟内，按下家用无线路由器的</span><span> WPS </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">按钮，直至无线路由器的</span><span> WPS </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">指示灯变为闪烁状态，再松开。完成后，电视画面将显示连网成功。无线路由器的</span><span> WPS </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">指示灯将由闪烁变为常亮。</span><span></span> \n</p>\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31133\" alt=\"\" /> \n<p style=\"text-indent:-3.0cm;\">\n\t<span><span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>步骤 1<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 步骤4 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">配置完成</span><span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">此时，您可以去手机应用市场选择下载</span><span>“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">华为随心控</span><span>”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">应用程序，使用手机控制秘盒。您也可以跳过该步骤，以后再下载或者进入秘盒设置界面选择其他下载方式。</span><span></span> \n</p>\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31134\" alt=\"\" /> \n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"884","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1397115590000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M3,MediaQ M310","visitedTimes":179,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}